1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What comes next will test your ability to associate information.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:09,000
Different operations will appear on screen, and you must complete them.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:13,840
To do this, you will have to add the number on your token to the one on the terminal.

4
00:00:13,840 --> 00:00:18,440
When the combination is correct, the operation will be solved.

5
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:21,560
You will need to clear two phases to advance.

6
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,640
A single mistake will reset the phase.

7
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:28,160
It will also reset if you repeat an operation that was already solved.

8
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,960
Or if the timer reaches zero.

9
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:33,160
Coordinate well, that will be the key.
